net.ligreto
Class ResultStatus

java.lang.Object
  net.ligreto.ResultStatus

public class ResultStatus
extends java.lang.Object

The class representing the result status of ligreto operations. It contains the various properties that are reported by individual operations.

Author:
Julius Stroffek
